subject: Dear valued beneficiary
body:
Dear valued beneficiary
You are advised to respond to this e-message today should you need more intel on the most appropriate and easiest way to receive your long overdue funds within the shortest time possible.
Yours faithfully,
Joseph Webb,
Regional Head

subject: Re: Dear valued beneficiary
body:
Hello Joseph Webb,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm intrigued by your message and would like to know more about these overdue funds you mentioned. Could you please provide more details? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Leona
